snippet: Princeton’s football program is on the upswing, but mistakes cost the Tigers in their Ivy League matchup against the University of Pennsylvania.
abstract: College Football East Roundup; Pennsylvania defeats Princeton, 28-21, continuing their decades-long winning streak in the matchup; other results noted.
lead_paragraph: Princeton’s football program is on the upswing, but mistakes cost the Tigers in their Ivy League matchup against the University of Pennsylvania.

headline.print_headline: On Verge of a Rare Victory Over Penn, Princeton Sees It Slip Away
